  "detailed_description": "Troid Blaster is a physics based asteroids roguelike with permadeath and perks<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* Random Levels- different each time.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* 10 different ships to buy and fly<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* 5 different zones with different asteroid types<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* Physics based system making game play much more dynamic<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* Endless mode levels to unlock<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* 360 controller support<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* PermaDeath<br />\r\n<br />\r\n(Exit to windows via button in top left of main menu screen)",
